# Pack It Up — Cursor Rules

## What this is
Pixel-art moving game. Player walks through apartment rooms and packs/sells/donates furniture. Personal motivation tool. No backend, no database, no UI libraries.

## File map
```
artifacts/pack-it-up/src/
  BedroomSlice.jsx    ← THE ENTIRE GAME (~3,300 lines)
  main.tsx            ← 15-line entry point only
  layout.json         ← furniture positions (x/y/scale) per room
  sell.mp3            ← sell chime
  assets/Cat-Sheet.png ← cat sprite sheet
  dev/spritePreview.jsx ← dev tool only (?preview=bed)
```

